channel.description:
Welcome to my The Last Era Project
[b]~Note~[/b]: [u][b]This isn't [s]Delta[/s], It's Devolution.[/b][/u]
This is a Server, with bosses, skilling, never used areas, etc. [u][b] Trying to make a 'Unique Server' [/b][/u]
This is a [b]317 client[/b] loading [b]377 cache[/b], that's the client.
Base: [u][b]Final Devolution 2.7[/b][/u]
[b] ~Latest Updates~[/b] [b] [b][color=blue]*[/color][/b]Added the "[u]Shade Boss[/u]"[/b]
[b]*[/b][b]85% DONE with [u]Skilling Island[/u][/b]
What I am going to do next:
